<emphasis id="B92D524AF5310E0660A6FD1DFE8EFD0B" bold="true" box="[199,352,655,680]" pageId="10" pageNumber="561">Distribution.</emphasis>
Southeastern 
<collectingCountry id="F34ECEC8F5310E06619EFD1DFDA9FD0B" box="[511,583,655,680]" name="Brazil" pageId="10" pageNumber="561">Brazil</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BE68E58F5310E0660A6FD26FBB2FD6F" blockId="10.[151,1437,151,789]" box="[199,1116,692,717]" pageId="10" pageNumber="561">
<emphasis id="B92D524AF5310E0660A6FD26FDCBFD6E" bold="true" box="[199,549,692,717]" pageId="10" pageNumber="561">Derivation of specific epithet.</emphasis>
Named for Brazilian phoridologist Danilo Ament.
